headline.main: Oil Prices Fall on Doubts Over Russian Output Curbs
headline.print_headline: Oil Prices Fall on Doubts Over Russian Output Curbs

lead_paragraph: Oil prices slipped in Asian trade on Monday, wiping out some of the gains of the previous session amid ongoing concern over Russia's compliance with a global deal to cut oil output.
